@@TJvPreviewRenderGraphics.Images
Summary
  A collection of images to render.
Description
  Use Images to add and modify the images to preview. At design time, click the ellipsis button in the
  Object Inspector to show the collection editor. Use the editor to add and modify the images in the
  collection.
