@@TJvPreviewRenderControl
<TITLEIMG TJvPreviewRenderControl>
#JVCLInfo
<GROUP JVCL.Printing>
<FLAG Component>
Summary
  Renders a preview of a TControl descendant.
Description
  Use TJvPreviewRenderControl when you want to render a TControl descendant (visual control) in a
