@@TJvPreviewPrinter.Assign
Summary
  Copies the properties of a compatible object to this object
Description
  Call Assign to copy the properties of a TJvPreviewPrinter or a TPrintDialog to this object. If
  Source is a TPrintDialog the Collate, Copies, FromPage, Options, PrintRange and ToPage properties
  are copied.
Parameters
  Source - The object to copy from
See Also
  <DELPHILINK TPrintDialog>

