@@TJvCustomPreviewRenderer
Summary
  Base class for components that can render a print preview on a TJvCustomPreviewControl.
Description
  Use TJvCustomPreviewRenderer as a base class to derive from when you want to create components that
  can render a print preview. Override the abstract DoAddPage to create a print preview page by page.

